        public int compareTableCellText(Selenium.Locator type,
                                String locator,
                                int elementMatch,
                                int row,
                                int col,
                                String text)
                         throws IOException
        compares the text of expected table cell with the actual table cell text of a table with from a table element
        Parameters:
